Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,人終難免一死？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must we die?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙中有沒有長生不死的生物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are there beings in the cosmos who live forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可以永遠逍遙地游在時間之河上？\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}afloat on an endless journey down the river of time?
